Author: crustyilex
Text: I'm trying to use low cal protein shakes as meal replacement. Along with volumous salads.   Also I have just started using a tracker, to count the days I don't do it. Even If i only go without it for a few hours.  Trying to view food as gym and mind fuel. Also clear out your ig feed. If their posts dont make YOU feel good about yourself, unfollow. Nothing personal, youre just looking out for you.
